# Pre-Merge Check Runbook (.mrd)

## Purpose
Ensure every branch is thoroughly validated before merging.

## Checklist
- [ ] All code builds and runs locally
- [ ] Run `vercel build` (or Vercel SDK local build) to simulate production
- [ ] All tests and linters pass (`npm run test`, `npm run lint`, `tsc --noEmit`)
- [ ] Review all new/changed files for clarity and completeness
- [ ] Write a thorough, descriptive commit message
- [ ] Update AGENTS.md and/or TASKS.md if any practices or requirements have changed
- [ ] Validate the RSS feed (if episode or feed changes)
- [ ] Ensure documentation is up to date

## Notes
- Only merge after all items are checked and confirmed.
